text: Although it had a polarizing effect i thought it was well crafted, well acted and tension filled thriller. What worked here are performances, some nice chemistry between the characters and that unerving sense of anticipation of what is going to happen next.  What did not work were some pacing issues, few contrived little things and the third act which took the movie downspiral. There were some interesting plot points that i did not see coming and really good message about how people should not act before they think, plus how senseless greedy corporations have become as they always stomp on little man. It is disposable thriller, not in the big guys league, but it will provide you with entertaining 90 minutes. 3,5/5
